<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/roddy-miller> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Roddy joined Sellafield Ltd in March 2022 as head of retrievals value stream. Prior to joining Sellafield Ltd, he enjoyed a diverse career with over 20 years’ experience leading project and programme portfolios and business transformations across Europe, Middle East, and Asia.  This experience has been gained through a range of senior and executive roles supporting nuclear and other highly regulated sectors. Roddy was appointed Chief Operating Officer in 2024."@en <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/rdfa> .
